		<RichText x="66" y="1224" width="419" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兽王加冕：3次特化次数盾，仅能使用兽境犬首击破，需要3只，击破后瘫痪黄金王兽10s。<br/>兽境犬首：<span color="#ffe599">75岩</span><span>充能盾，岩攻击</span><span color="#ffe599">+25</span><span>/次，非岩攻击</span><span color="#ffe599">+2</span><span>/次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="65" y="597" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffe599" width="309" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
