		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽蓄力向地面冲去，在地面进行8字形擦地移动，碰到造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽蓄力，贴近地面喷吐渊之岩，接触持续造成<span color="#ffe599">50%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害，可与某些技能形成连招。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="671" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽升空停顿，连续召唤3个「黄金犬首」追踪玩家，每个犬首造成<span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽飞到高空，高速下落坠入地面造成巨大范围的<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害，片刻后钻出，造成</span><span color="#ceffbf">无侵蚀</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害，随后在场地内产生9个小岩喷造成</span><span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">由黄金王兽召唤的「兽境犬首」，其会周期性喷吐蓝色的「渊弹」，「渊弹」发射1s后开始追踪玩家，碰到造成<span color="#bababa">12.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="433" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兽境类原魔造成的伤害都会附带「侵蚀」效果。黄金王兽的效果为：每层每秒扣除玩家<span color="#ffe599">(1%HP+25)</span><span>的生命值，每层持续</span><span color="#ffe599">9.5s</span><span>，持续时间独立计算，可叠加。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="1151" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽在破盾眩晕后起身旋会击飞附近的玩家，造成<span color="#ceffbf">无侵蚀</span><span>的</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽移至场地中央，获得<span textDecoration="underline">兽王加冕</span><span>，进入</span><span color="#ffeebf">嗜魔</span><span>状态，外观发生变化，并于场地边缘安置3个「兽境犬首」，若被该犬首命中则造成</span><span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害，嗜魔后的黄金王兽的</span><span color="#ff9999">攻击力提升30%。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽原地开始旋转，形成巨大的龙卷风，在场地内来游动，碰到造成<span color="#ffe599">50%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害，旋转结束时会额外造成</span><span color="#ffe599">12.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽升空，在空中悬停一会后立即使用尾部扫击，造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
